Sanctificávit Dóminus * tabernáculum suum: quia hæc est domus Dei, in qua invocábitur nomen ejus, de quo scriptum est: Et erit nomen meum ibi, dicit Dóminus.
The Lord hath sanctified * his tabernacle. For this is the house of God, wherein his name shall be invoked, of which it is written: My Name shall be there, saith the Lord.
